{"tid":1332241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.21遊行獲發不反對通知書   警以安全為由拒金鐘或中環作終點","createTime":"2019-07-19T08:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T11:20:01.000Z","uid":48093,"like":8,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"99789d9a62ab676464834579ed295395d543efb4","tid":1332241,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563524985_f225.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563524985_f225.png&h=e62766e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣於本周日7.21再次發起反送中大遊行，並於今日收到警方不反對通知書，遊行原定以中環遮打道終審法院為終點，但警方以公共秩序安全為由，嚴格限制遊行終點必須設於灣仔盧押道與莊士敦道交界，不能以金鐘或中環作終站；且當日遊行必須於當晚9點結束，有別於過往定於晚上11時59分。警方也企硬只開放軒尼詩道西行3線及兩條電車路，拒絕開放軒尼詩道6條行車線。<br />\n<br />\n7.21遊行將於下午3時集合起步，在銅鑼灣維園出發。民陣在6.9及6.16亦曾發起反送中遊行，有103萬及200萬人參與。"},{"pid":"3f4400830a6ccb30631030a6092852f79962dd80","tid":1332241,"uid":282149,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347233c52500d874a7bbf5f9e1a1fbb725704047","tid":1332241,"uid":128569,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"九點都未行完咁點"},{"pid":"da1dc1ce661d58c0aba8760d10cede5fffd1104d","tid":1332241,"uid":143701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"875900e4d27d43b483ba2f92e9f6c20947b6bf54","tid":1332241,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n7.21和理非都要全gear！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoIDfCHlS-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPoIDfCHlS-8&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=46a9a198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoIDfCHlS-8</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔帶gear既下場就係你隔離個個比人搞都救唔番</span><br />\n<br />\n7.21前學下武功：<br />\n<br />\n<em>游蕙禎做Youtuber 教大家應付扑頭狗</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332096/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332096/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n補充下心態：<br />\n<em>等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n得閒做下文宣AIRDROP：<br />\n<em>[721 線上文宣 2.0] 全港最大型既線上文宣2.0 正式上線</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1331663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1331663/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n7.21見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f51105c271da607614976fb7c78d01d4bb630b0","tid":1332241,"uid":23707,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"似逼人出喎"},{"pid":"723dbf1630f6c183243ab9ff9c28ca2cd22c8fe1","tid":1332241,"uid":10905,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"好囉<br />\n最怕你唔限我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095fb5c03a264cae4f92be6f5add4d1917a5f506","tid":1332241,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a49fc4c95ad4e8dac637c05011c10590e2b1810","tid":1332241,"uid":94968,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08