要全gear！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoIDfCHlS-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPoIDfCHlS-8&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=46a9a198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoIDfCHlS-8</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔帶gear既下場就係你隔離個個比人搞都救唔番</span><br />\n<br />\n7.21前學下武功：<br />\n<br />\n<em>游蕙禎做Youtuber 教大家應付扑頭狗</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332096/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332096/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n補充下心態：<br />\n<em>等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n得閒做下文宣AIRDROP：<br />\n<em>[721 線上文宣 2.0] 全港最大型既線上文宣2.0 正式上線</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1331663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1331663/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n7.21見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"721 新香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要說「721 要人」或「721 金鐘見」，試著說「721 新香港」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkjJqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkjJqS</a><br />\n<br />\n[70年大限] 有冇人諗住set個目標 要全力響9月30之前令共匪倒台?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/diKbzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/diKbzS</a><br />\n<br />\n[齊上齊落再開] 請深思 獨立vs臨時政府?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PQLuwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PQLuwU</a>"},{"pid":"7ac4370b2d7facf8fa5c98e08c525418e929024f","tid":1332241,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q